<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A <rs type="objectType">statue</rs> (for description see bibliography)  and <rs type="material">blue marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue  base</rs> with simple moulding above, broken below and to the right (<measure dim="height" unit="metre" type="length">0.25</measure> x <measure dim="width" unit="metre" type="length">0.57</measure> x <measure dim="depth" unit="metre" type="length">0.28</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>i. <rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face of the base; ii inscribed on the plinth of the statue.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>i.: Letters square, probably third century; <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.04</measure></p><p>ii: cursive, l.1, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03</measure>; l.2. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.025</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date cert="low" notAfter="0300" notBefore="0200">Third century</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">sculpture</rs>)
</p>
</div>
